%h2 Edit Confirmation Email

%hr

%p
  %b All confirmation emails will have the following team info above the editable message:<br />
  Team name: TEAM NAME<br />
  Position: ###<br />
  Class: CATEGORY<br />
  Shirt sizes: SIZES<br />
  \---

= form_for @site, url: admin_confirmation_email_path do |form|
  .field
    = form.label :confirmation_email_body, "Message"
    = form.text_area :confirmation_email_body, class: "confirmation-message"

  .actions-field
    %input.save(type="submit" value="Save Confirmation Email")
    = link_to "Cancel", :back, class: "cancel"

